    <briefdescription>
<para>Represents a decimal value using an integer scaled by 10^precision. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Internally stores the decimal as an integer multiplied by 10^precision. Example: raw_value = 12345, precision = 2 =&gt; decimal value 123.45 </para>
    </detaileddescription>
